      "finding": "The paper oscillates between presenting results as conditional on assumptions and drawing general conclusions about LLM limitations. For example, the abstract states 'confidence accumulated through repeated self-evaluation reflects the shared failure structure rather than independently accumulated evidence' without the crucial qualification that this is conditional on the joint independence assumption. Similar unqualified statements appear throughout.",
